name: Christina Hendricks
description:
I know, it has been done over and over... but not as a LoRA yet. So here it is, hope Aitrepreneur will be happy with the results of this model.

Use kohya-ss/sd-webui-additional-networks (github.com) in auto1111 to load the LoRA model. You can combine it with other LoRA for blended poses.

modelVersions.name: v2.0-mr
modelVersions.description:
Multi-resolution model from the same dataset as v1.0 but leveragind 384x384, 448x448 and 512x512 resolution of the same 16 source images.

I also disables 8bitsadam because I discovered that models tend to look better when not using it... Multi-Resolution models are supposed, in theory, to produce better faces and details when the subject is smaller in the overall picture.

So you are the judge if v2 is better than v1.
